  "identifier": "HB 785",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to solar farms in the Commonwealth.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 138 to define \"owner,\" \"solar farm,\" and \"taxes\"; levy an excise tax on the owner of a solar farm in Kentucky at an annual rate of $200 per acre for land used to generate electricity; provide for a yearly increase of the tax rate based on the change of the consumer price index; specify reporting and payment requirements; establish penalties.",
